title: America_9-11_We_Will_Never_Forget_DVD_Tufavideo
description:
We now know much more on the September-11-event, 
and the simple fact that almost all parts of the Event is
beyond the limits that can be implemented in the physical 
reality, sticks out. 
Due to this it has been concluded that all so-called
Sept-11-videos are pre-produced fakes. 
(Most videos are fake on own merits.)

We include here the
America 9/11 --- We Will Never Forget 
DVD that is credited to CameraPlanet.com

We recommend a selective download, as a large part of the torrent
consists of AVI files, that is taken from the DVD.

This is also the absolutely most boring and uninteresting 9/11 film
encountered so forth. Consists mostly of actors telling their story
on camera.

Produced by Spectrum Films

Tufa 2014
